Output deck/public/videos/mac-beta/01-install-launch.mp4
Set Shell zsh
Set Width 1440
Set Height 900
Set FontSize 20
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono, JetBrainsMono, JetBrainsMono Nerd Font, JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono, monospace"
Set Framerate 10
Set CursorBlink false


Sleep 1s

Type "brew tap wendylabsinc/tap"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "brew install --cask wendy-agent"
Enter
Sleep 12s

Ctrl+L
Sleep 500ms

Type "open /Applications/WendyAgentMac.app"
Enter
Sleep 5s
